{"tid":2377083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人大常委會會議閉幕未提反制BN(O)政策","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T11:38:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87767eed0b77a16ecf186b7ab7301bbe172bda62","tid":2377083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/22200042/image1611316767759.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F22200042%2Fimage1611316767759.png&h=1162a7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會會議今日在北京閉幕，早前有報道稱，中央將在會上通過對英國BN(O)移民計劃的反制措施，包括禁止BN(O)持有人出任公職，全國人大常委譚耀宗今日接受傳媒查詢時表示，會上沒有與香港相關議程，又稱不想猜測中央有何應對行動及措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/321770/人大常委會會議閉幕未提反制bno政策%E3%80%80譚耀宗遞港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F321770%2F%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%96%89%E5%B9%95%E6%9C%AA%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6bno%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%25E3%2580%2580%E8%AD%9A%E8%80%80%E5%AE%97%E9%81%9E%E6%B8%AF%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=f50f8b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/321770/人大常委會會議閉幕未提反制bno政策%E3%80%80譚耀宗遞港/</a>"},{"pid":"e5fdd7c0638518f54ebd2922d032f72edde9c5b8","tid":2377083,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2907f0dc7eb19533b09407158e3c0361b3fa3f1d","tid":2377083,"uid":236623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87767eed0b77a16ecf186b7ab7301bbe172bda62","tid":2377083,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:00:3